params.sqlcmd: "select " +" M_WS.\\"WS_CD\\" as \\"WS_CD\\", " +" M_WS.\\"WS_CD\\" as \\"h_WS_CD\\", " +" M_WS.\\"WS_NAME\\" as \\"WS_NAME\\", " +" M_WS.\\"WS_TEL\\" as \\"WS_TEL\\", " +" M_WS.\\"WS_PERSON\\" as \\"WS_PERSON\\", " +" M_WS.\\"WH_CD\\" as \\"WH_CD\\", " +" M_WS.\\"SUB_WS_CD\\" as \\"SUB_WS_CD\\", " +" M_WS.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\", " +" sub_M_WS.\\"WS_NAME\\" as \\"SUB_WS_NAME\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_NAME\\" as \\"WH_NAME\\", " +" M_WS.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_WS M_WS, " +" M_WS sub_M_WS, " +" M_WH " +"where " +" M_WS.WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD(+) " +" and M_WS.\\"SUB_WS_CD\\" = sub_M_WS.\\"WS_CD\\"(+) " +" and M_WS.\\"WS_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" M_WS.\\"WS_CD\\" as \\"WS_CD\\", " +" M_WS.\\"WS_NAME\\" as \\"WS_NAME\\", " +" M_WS.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_WS " +"where " +" M_WS.\\"WS_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_WH.\\"WH_CD\\" as \\"WH_CD\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_NAME\\" as \\"WH_NAME\\", " +" M_WH.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_TYP\\" as \\"WH_TYP\\" " +"from " +" M_WH " +"where " +" M_WH.\\"WH_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" M_WS.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" M_WS.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_WS " +"where " +" M_WS.\\"WS_CD\\" = ? " +"for update nowait"
"SELECT " +" CLASS_NAME " +"FROM " +" M_CLASS " +"WHERE " +" CLASS_CD1 = '40' " +" AND CLASS_CD2 = '01' " +" AND CLASS_CD3 = '00'"
"SELECT " +" CLASS_NAME " +"FROM " +" M_CLASS " +"WHERE " +" CLASS_CD1 = '40' " +" AND CLASS_CD2 = '01' " +" AND CLASS_CD3 = ?"
